//	StartMonth: Month the event starts on, 1-12
//	StartDay: Day the event starts on, 1-31
// ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
//	StartYear, StartMonth and StartDay values configured in the file getting inserted into
